item.title: IC Volleyball hit back against a disorganised LSE
item.author: Ines Ullmo,Julian Macron,
item.description: This Wednesday IC Volleyball Club was scheduled to play London School of Economics in both ladies’ and men’s but at different venues. Early in the week the two fixtures seemed destined to cancellation after a lack of referees in Greater London hit both clubs. After relentless efforts from committee …
